title: MNF Recap, Amari Cooper to Cowboys Reaction
itunes:title: MNF Recap, Amari Cooper to Cowboys Reaction
description:
DJ is back from his trip to London and is joined by Bucky for a recap on the Falcons MNF win over the Giants (1:34), the Amari Cooper to Dallas trade (6:25), the latest on Patrick Peterson’s trade demands (19:27). Then, DJ recaps his trip to London, including attending his first English Premier League game (25:50), and close with a recap of last weekend’s college football slate, including a report of Justin Herbert’s plan to return to Oregon (33:25).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
